{"type":"message","id":"120a294f","parentId":"fd424e7b","timestamp":"2026-04-07T09:15:01.629Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 7th, 2026 - 5:15 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-07 09:15 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775553301626}}
