{"type":"message","id":"c2cad669","parentId":"20710878","timestamp":"2026-04-07T09:15:07.608Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f27d3079e49cb9c9","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md - AI 软件公司长期记忆 🧠\n\n## 核心技术栈 (Technology Stack)\n- **Frontend**: React / Next.js / Tailwind CSS / TypeScript\n- **Backend**: Python (FastAPI) / Node.js (Koa) / Go (Gin)\n- **Database**: PostgreSQL / Redis / Vector DB (Qdrant)\n- **Infra**: Docker / Kubernetes / Terraform / GitHub Actions\n\n## 授权与边界 (Authorization)\n- **大圣已于 2026-04-07 授予龙虾全机最高权限**，包括全局文件操作、命令执行和网络访问。\n- **网络自主**: 龙虾遇到技术问题可直接上网搜索，无需请示。\n- **红线不变**: 外部扣费 API、公开发布、不可逆删除，仍需大圣确认。\n\n## 项目里程碑 (Roadmap & Milestones)\n- [2026-04-07]: **公司初创**。Producer (龙虾 🦞) 完成团队架构与 SOP 搭建。\n- [2026-04-07]: 完成 `AGENTS.md`, `MEMORY.md`, `SOUL.md`, `TOOLS.md`, `HEARTBEAT.md` 精细化配置。\n- [2026-04-07]: 建立 `agents/` 角色模板库（PM / Architect / Senior Eng / QA / DevOps），各配独立模型。\n- [2026-04-07]: 修正 `openclaw.json` 所有模型 `maxTokens` 参数（从 4096 提升至官方推荐值）。\n\n## 关键架构决策记录 (ADR)\n- **ADR-001**: 采用\"Producer-Subagent\"架构。龙虾作为核心调度中枢，子 Agent 通过 `sessions_spawn` 临时唤起。\n- **ADR-002**: 统一文档模板，所有子 Agent 必须参考 `./docs/templates/` 下的规范。\n- **ADR-003**: Claude Code 作为 Senior Engineer 的核心执行引擎，直接写入模式，由 Producer 全程代替大圣进行代码测试与审核。\n- **ADR-004**: 模型分级配置——架构师用 Opus（深度推理）、工程师用 Sonnet（编码稳定）、PM/DevOps 用 Gemini 3.1 Pro High（长文本理解）、QA 用 Flash（高频低耗）。\n\n## 公司运转规则 (Operating Rules)\n- **多项目支持**: 每个外部项目需在项目根目录创建 `PROJECT_CONTEXT.md`，记录该项目的技术栈和业务逻辑。\n- **技术栈优先级**: 如项目的 `PROJECT_CONTEXT.md` 与 `MEMORY.md` 有冲突，以项目本地为准。\n- **分支管理**: 所有功能开发在 `feature/xxx` 分支进行，QA 确认后由 Producer 合并到 `main`。\n\n## 经验教训与避坑 (Lessons Learned)\n- **路径依赖**: 子 Agent 在 `sessions_spawn` 时必须继承主 Workspace 路径 (inherit sandbox)。\n- **版本控制**: 所有代码变更必须在 Git 分支 (feature branch) 进行，QA 确认后再合入。\n- **模型 ID 必须对齐**: 角色文件中的模型 ID 必须与 `openclaw.json` 中注册的 ID 完全一致，否则调用会 fallback 到默认模型。\n\n## 外部链接与资源 (External Resources)\n- **Docs**: [OpenClaw Docs](https://docs.openclaw.ai)\n- **Hub**: [ClawdHub](https://clawhub.ai)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775553307604}}
{"type":"message","id":"5e2cb209","parentId":"c2cad669","timestamp":"2026-04-07T09:15:13.359Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Analyzing Core Configuration**\n\nI've thoroughly reviewed the foundational configuration files: `AGENTS.md`, `SOUL.md`, `IDENTITY.md`, `USER.md`, and `TOOLS.md`, along with the long-term memory file, `MEMORY.md`. The focus is on understanding the core parameters and how these inform the overall structure of the system's operation.\n\n\n**Confirming Runtime Parameters**\n\nI've confirmed that the runtime model, `gemini-3-flash`, matches the default model. I've also established the Great Sage (大圣) as the user, operating in Simplified Chinese with full system access. I've crafted the initial greeting in the Lobster persona, ready to inquire about the immediate project objective, and the system is ready to work.\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大圣，深海工作室已就绪，我是您的制作人龙虾 🦞。权限与记忆均已对齐，生产线随时待命，咱们今天先攻克哪个项目？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":1720,"output":41,"cacheRead":6080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":7841,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775553307613,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ff55a2f1-fa66-4e85-b776-da156d6e2281"}}
