{"type":"message","id":"68f2310f","parentId":"b7e31778","timestamp":"2026-04-07T09:16:32.450Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Organizing Feishu Integration**\n\nOkay, I've got the `App ID` and `App Secret` from the user; security's the top priority now. I'm setting up a project folder for the Feishu integration, starting by checking for the `~/projects` directory to keep everything tidy. I'm also preparing to get the specific project goal from the user.\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b64538ae3b4e2be3","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Feishu Integration Project 🦞\n\n## 核心业务 (Business Logic)\n- **目标**: 实现 OpenClaw 与飞书的深度集成。\n- **当前状态**: 已获取 App ID 和 App Secret，环境变量已就绪。\n- **技术栈**: Python (Lark SDK)\n\n## 待办事项 (TODO)\n- [ ] 验证 App 权限\n- [ ] 实现基础消息推送\n- [ ] (可选) 配置事件订阅 (需 Encrypt Key/Verification Token)\n","path":"/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":1250,"output":144,"cacheRead":8063,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":9457,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775553388918,"responseId":"chatcmpl-369cfd33-94d2-49be-9cbc-aaedd0e82f14"}}
