 Token 獲取成功！\n⚠️ 詳情獲取失敗: {\"code\":99991672,\"msg\":\"Access denied. One of the following scopes is required: [admin:app.info:readonly, application:application:self_manage].应用尚未开通所需的应用身份权限：[admin:app.info:readonly, application:application:self_manage]，点击链接申请并开通任一权限即可：https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a95e7a8914ba5cc2/auth?q=admin:app.info:readonly,application:application:self_manage&op_from=openapi&token_type=tenant\",\"error\":{\"permission_violations\":[{\"type\":\"action_scope_required\",\"subject\":\"admin:app.info:readonly\"},{\"subject\":\"application:application:self_manage\",\"type\":\"action_scope_required\"}],\"message\":\"Refer to the documentation to fix the error: https://open.feishu.cn/document/uAjLw4CM/ugTN1YjL4UTN24CO1UjN/trouble-shooting/how-to-fix-the-99991672-error\",\"log_id\":\"202604071718092BCE8F2432F288F400E4\",\"troubleshooter\":\"排查建议查看(Troubleshooting suggestions): https://open.feishu.cn/search?from=openapi&log_id=202604071718092BCE8F2432F288F400E4&code=99991672&method_id=6944687146168287259\"}}","cwd":"/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775553489297}}
{"type":"message","id":"df25e085","parentId":"2c2a449b","timestamp":"2026-04-07T09:18:13.451Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"测试报告出来了，大圣！🦞\n\n**结论：Key 是有效的，但权限需要手动点一下。**\n\n1. **验证通过**：我已经成功通过您的 `App ID` 和 `App Secret` 换取到了飞书的 `Tenant Access Token`，这证明账号信息完全正确！\n2. **阻碍点**：目前这个 App 还没有开通“读取应用信息”的权限，所以我去查它叫什么名字时被飞书拦截了。\n\n**大圣需要做的（二选一）：**\n- **方案 A（推荐）**：点击下方链接，直接给这个 App 加上基础权限（然后点“发布版本”）：\n  [点击申请并开通权限](https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a95e7a8914ba5cc2/auth?q=admin:app.info:readonly,application:application:self_manage)\n- **方案 B（直接开干）**：如果您已经知道要给谁发消息（比如某个群号 `chat_id` 或您的 `user_id`），我可以直接写**发送消息**的脚本，那个权限（`im:message:send_as_bot`）通常是机器人最基础的。\n\n**下一步您想？**\n1. 我等您开通权限后再测一次。\n2. 直接告诉我一个群机器人 Webhook，或者您的 OpenID / ChatID，我直接给您发个“龙虾问候”。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":6604,"output":324,"cacheRead":8040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14968,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775553489303,"responseId":"chatcmpl-677f0374-c110-4b50-9ec5-fa9ccad7db4e"}}
