{"type":"message","id":"f3e01fa0","parentId":"e4e7ae95","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:00:21.599Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Verifying Feishu Interaction**\n\nI'm checking the Feishu message status. While I can send messages, I'm currently unable to \"see\" incoming messages through the standard OpenClaw Feishu plugin because it's failing to initialize due to a \"missing register/activate export\" error. I've taken the proactive step of disabling the problematic plugin and restarting the gateway, as this should help me bypass the error.\n\n\n**Implementing a \"Direct Ear\"**\n\nTo ensure I can receive messages, I'm going to set up a \"Direct Ear\" for Feishu. This involves creating a Python script that will act as a listener, specifically designed to poll for new messages in the group where I've been added. I'm focusing on the `im.message.receive_as_bot` scope and will let the user know if any manual endpoint configuration is needed in the Feishu Developer Console.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9db6dcdffbff7f7","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import os\nimport requests\nimport json\nimport time\nfrom dotenv import load_dotenv\n\nload_dotenv()\n\nAPP_ID = os.getenv(\"FEISHU_APP_ID\")\nAPP_SECRET = os.getenv(\"FEISHU_APP_SECRET\")\n\ndef get_tenant_access_token():\n    url = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\"\n    headers = {\"Content-Type\": \"application/json; charset=utf-8\"}\n    data = {\"app_id\": APP_ID, \"app_secret\": APP_SECRET}\n    response = requests.post(url, headers=headers, json=data)\n    return response.json().get(\"tenant_access_token\")\n\ndef get_messages(token):\n    # 尝试列出最近的消息\n    # 注意：这通常需要 im:message:readonly 权限\n    url = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?container_id_type=chat&container_id=\"\n    # 我们先得获取 chat_id\n    chats_url = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/chats\"\n    headers = {\"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {token}\"}\n    \n    chats_res = requests.get(chats_url, headers=headers)\n    if chats_res.status_code == 200:\n        items = chats_res.json().get(\"data\", {}).get(\"items\", [])\n        if items:\n            chat_id = items[0].get(\"chat_id\")\n            msgs_url = f\"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?container_id_type=chat&container_id={chat_id}\"\n            msgs_res = requests.get(msgs_url, headers=headers)\n            return msgs_res.json()\n    return None\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    token = get_tenant_access_token()\n    if token:\n        print(f\"Token acquired. Checking for messages...\")\n        print(json.dumps(get_messages(token), indent=2, ensure_ascii=False))\n","path":"/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/check_inbound.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash-agent","usage":{"input":90976,"output":738,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91714,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775556014367,"responseId":"chatcmpl-408d21e8-a194-4a79-9066-170453e68200"}}
