{"type":"message","id":"94b72ebc","parentId":"b7fd937f","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:02:48.517Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Initiating Plugin Repair**\n\nGreat, I'm diving into Plan A! 🦞 I'm taking charge of fixing the Feishu plugin at `/Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/index.js`. The goal is to address those \"missing register/activate export\" errors. I'll start by examining the `index.js` file to understand its current export structure and determine the best way to implement the necessary `register` and `activate` functions.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_974a51fadeca6fce","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/index.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash-agent","usage":{"input":11042,"output":154,"cacheRead":80846,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92042,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775556164060,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3f929abe-0e65-427f-a112-65d1bbc213fa"}}
