{"type":"message","id":"fccfa3b0","parentId":"12930703","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:04:23.932Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a3d616264448a2fc","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Config invalid\nFile: ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\nProblem:\n  - <root>: read failed: TypeError: Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'specifier')\n\nRun: openclaw doctor --fix\nGateway aborted: config is invalid.\n<root>: read failed: TypeError: Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'specifier')\nFix the config and retry, or run \"openclaw doctor\" to repair.\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":3836,"aggregated":"Config invalid\nFile: ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\nProblem:\n  - <root>: read failed: TypeError: Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'specifier')\n\nRun: openclaw doctor --fix\nGateway aborted: config is invalid.\n<root>: read failed: TypeError: Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'specifier')\nFix the config and retry, or run \"openclaw doctor\" to repair.\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775556263926}}
{"type":"message","id":"603dc717","parentId":"fccfa3b0","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:04:27.919Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Resolving Plugin Error**\n\nI'm hitting a \"TypeError: Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'specifier')\" error. 🦞 I've decided to drop the `defineBundledChannelEntry` wrapper since it might be expecting something I'm not providing. Instead, I'll export a standard plugin object with `register` and `activate` functions. This should fix the issue and get the Feishu channel up and running.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fc08eeff71341af4","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/index.js","content":"async function register(api) {\n\tconst { registerFeishuChannel } = await import(\"./channel-entry.js\");\n\treturn registerFeishuChannel(api);\n}\n\nasync function activate(api) {\n\tconst { activateFeishuChannel } = await import(\"./channel-entry.js\");\n\treturn activateFeishuChannel(api);\n}\n\nconst feishu_default = {\n\tid: \"feishu\",\n\tname: \"Feishu\",\n\tdescription: \"OpenClaw Feishu/Lark channel plugin\",\n\tregister,\n\tactivate\n};\n\nexport {\n\tactivate,\n\tfeishu_default as default,\n\tregister\n};\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash-agent","usage":{"input":13141,"output":287,"cacheRead":80690,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94118,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775556263936,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8b87931f-1dfe-4503-8f3e-4794250b93d4"}}
