{"type":"message","id":"4de18b1d","parentId":"9ca10cd5","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:09:45.408Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Standardizing Communication Language**\n\nI'm switching to Chinese for all future communications. 🦞 I'm also providing an update on the Feishu plugin status: it's still being repaired and isn't showing up yet. I'm focusing on providing direct results and will let the user know as soon as the plugin is functional.\n\n\n**Verifying Feishu Integration**\n\nThe Feishu plugin is still facing initialization issues, so I'm taking a different approach. I've developed a custom \"Proxy Bot\" script that bypasses the plugin and directly connects to Feishu. This script will listen for messages and relay them to me, and I'll use it to send a test message to the group to confirm that everything's working as expected.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e4f4d15c2d5f1ac","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/final_test.py","content":"import os\nimport requests\nimport json\nfrom dotenv import load_dotenv\n\nload_dotenv()\n\nAPP_ID = os.getenv(\"FEISHU_APP_ID\")\nAPP_SECRET = os.getenv(\"FEISHU_APP_SECRET\")\n\ndef get_tenant_access_token():\n    url = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\"\n    headers = {\"Content-Type\": \"application/json; charset=utf-8\"}\n    data = {\"app_id\": APP_ID, \"app_secret\": APP_SECRET}\n    response = requests.post(url, headers=headers, json=data)\n    return response.json().get(\"tenant_access_token\")\n\ndef send_message(token, chat_id, text):\n    url = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?receive_id_type=chat_id\"\n    headers = {\n        \"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {token}\",\n        \"Content-Type\": \"application/json; charset=utf-8\"\n    }\n    data = {\n        \"receive_id\": chat_id,\n        \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n        \"content\": json.dumps({\"text\": text})\n    }\n    res = requests.post(url, headers=headers, json=data)\n    return res.json()\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    token = get_tenant_access_token()\n    # 先获取 chat_id\n    chats_url = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/chats\"\n    headers = {\"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {token}\"}\n    chats_res = requests.get(chats_url, headers=headers).json()\n    \n    if chats_res.get(\"code\") == 0:\n        items = chats_res.get(\"data\", {}).get(\"items\", [])\n        if items:\n            chat_id = items[0].get(\"chat_id\")\n            result = send_message(token, chat_id, \"大圣，这是来自龙虾的深度连通性测试报告：链路已复活！🦞\")\n            if result.get(\"code\") == 0:\n                print(\"✅ 飞书发送测试成功\")\n            else:\n                print(f\"❌ 飞书发送失败: {result.get('msg')}\")\n        else:\n            print(\"❌ 未发现已加入的群聊\")\n    else:\n        print(f\"❌ 获取群聊列表失败: {chats_res.get('msg')}\")\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash-agent","usage":{"input":5715,"output":795,"cacheRead":88742,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95252,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775556579286,"responseId":"chatcmpl-06e29480-9a6c-4c06-98a8-52e9ca6fb651"}}
