{"type":"message","id":"2dd8915d","parentId":"d34536e6","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:10:41.303Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Confirming Message Synchronization**\n\nI'm confirming that I can see the user's messages in this dialog box, as they're being synchronized through the current session. 🦞 This means our communication is uninterrupted, and I'm ready to continue our work.\n\n\n**Troubleshooting Feishu Integration**\n\nThe user is experiencing an issue where their Feishu messages aren't appearing in the OpenClaw Control UI. This is because the built-in Feishu channel plugin, which normally synchronizes messages between Feishu and OpenClaw, is currently broken and failing to load. My manual \"eavesdropping\" scripts have confirmed that messages are reaching the Feishu server, but they aren't being forwarded to the OpenClaw message stream. I'm investigating how to effectively bridge this gap.\n\n\n**Fixing Plugin Logic**\n\nThe \"TypeError: Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'specifier')\" was likely caused by the relative import `../../channel-entry-contract-DyY5TZkc.js`. I've corrected the path and am now adding the `register` and `activate` functions to the Feishu plugin, while ensuring they don't break existing functionality. I'll also double-check the `openclaw` log to confirm the plugin handles these functions correctly. 🦞\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_82774e7c63fec4","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/bridge_listener.py","content":"import os\nimport requests\nimport json\nimport time\nfrom dotenv import load_dotenv\n\nload_dotenv()\n\n# 常量配置\nAPP_ID = os.getenv(\"FEISHU_APP_ID\")\nAPP_SECRET = os.getenv(\"FEISHU_APP_SECRET\")\nGATEWAY_URL = \"http://127.0.0.1:18789/v1/messages\" # OpenClaw Gateway HTTP 入口\nAUTH_TOKEN = \"877fdff334d05e40750b7855de184089075849b55ba4600a\" # 从 openclaw.json 获取的 token\n\ndef get_tenant_access_token():\n    url = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\"\n    headers = {\"Content-Type\": \"application/json; charset=utf-8\"}\n    data = {\"app_id\": APP_ID, \"app_secret\": APP_SECRET}\n    response = requests.post(url, headers=headers, json=data)\n    return response.json().get(\"tenant_access_token\")\n\ndef poll_messages(token, last_msg_id=None):\n    # 获取 chat_id\n    chats_url = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/chats\"\n    headers = {\"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {token}\"}\n    chats_res = requests.get(chats_url, headers=headers).json()\n    \n    if chats_res.get(\"code\") != 0 or not chats_res.get(\"data\", {}).get(\"items\"):\n        return None, last_msg_id\n\n    chat_id = chats_res[\"data\"][\"items\"][0][\"chat_id\"]\n    msgs_url = f\"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?container_id_type=chat&container_id={chat_id}\"\n    msgs_res = requests.get(msgs_url, headers=headers).json()\n    \n    if msgs_res.get(\"code\") == 0:\n        messages = msgs_res.get(\"data\", {}).get(\"items\", [])\n        new_messages = []\n        for msg in messages:\n            # 只处理用户发出的文本消息\n            if msg.get(\"sender\", {}).get(\"sender_type\") == \"user\" and msg.get(\"msg_type\") == \"text\":\n                if not last_msg_id or msg.get(\"update_time\", \"\") > last_msg_id:\n                    new_messages.append({\n                        \"id\": msg.get(\"message_id\"),\n                        \"text\": json.loads(msg.get(\"content\")).get(\"text\"),\n                        \"time\": msg.get(\"update_time\")\n                    })\n        \n        if new_messages:\n            # 按时间排序并更新 last_msg_id\n            new_messages.sort(key=lambda x: x[\"time\"])\n            return new_messages, new_messages[-1][\"time\"]\n            \n    return None, last_msg_id\n\ndef bridge_to_openclaw(text):\n    # 尝试模拟 Webhook 发送给 OpenClaw\n    # 注意：这里的逻辑可能需要根据 OpenClaw 实际接口调整\n    print(f\"🌉 正在桥接消息到对话框: {text}\")\n    # 这里我们只是演示，实际上 OpenClaw 如果插件没挂载，外部很难直接插入对话流。\n    # 我们还是先用“龙虾汇报”的方式。\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    token = get_tenant_access_token()\n    last_id = str(int(time.time() * 1000)) # 只获取脚本启动之后的消息\n    print(f\"🦞 飞书监听器（龙虾版）已启动，开始实时同步...\")\n    \n    while True:\n        try:\n            msgs, last_id = poll_messages(token, last_id)\n            if msgs:\n                for m in msgs:\n                    print(f\"📥 收到飞书指令: {m['text']}\")\n                    # 在控制台打印出来，我（龙虾）就能在 shell 输出里看到\n            time.sleep(2)\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"⚠️ 监听出错: {e}\")\n            time.sleep(5)\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash-agent","usage":{"input":6375,"output":1328,"cacheRead":88725,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96428,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775556631678,"responseId":"chatcmpl-600fddeb-108e-404d-a738-69a088eab94b"}}
