{"type":"message","id":"028c1c30","parentId":"470bc209","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:12:39.901Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"最省流量、最直接的方式就是：**直接在这个网页对话框里跟我聊。** 🦞\n\n理由很简单：\n1. **零延迟**：网页框是长连接，消息秒到。飞书那边我得不断“轮询”服务器，既费流量又慢。\n2. **零干扰**：不用去管飞书那个坏掉的插件，咱们绕过它，直接通信。\n3. **最纯粹**：代码、架构图、执行结果在这里显示得最清楚。\n\n**龙虾的建议策略：**\n- **发令/看代码/聊方案**：全在这个网页框完成。\n- **进度通知**：我会顺便给飞书群里发个关键结论的推送（比如“任务已完成”），方便大圣在手机上随时瞟一眼。\n\n监听脚本已关，流量消耗降至最低。**大圣，咱们开工吧！第一个任务是什么？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash-agent","usage":{"input":15798,"output":204,"cacheRead":80653,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96655,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775556755112,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d809d9e3-fb2d-4fa8-96a8-b1a82826fd5a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"31a745ef","parentId":"028c1c30","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:14:23.255Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-04-07 18:14 GMT+8] 飞书是否有一个插件可以跟你对接的，而不是使用轮询这种低级的方式"}],"timestamp":1775556863250}}
{"type":"message","id":"f073ec44","parentId":"31a745ef","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:14:27.019Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Opting for the \"Webhook (Event Subscription)\" Approach**\n\nI'm moving forward with the **Webhook (Event Subscription)** approach for Feishu. 🦞 It's the most efficient and direct method, ensuring I'm notified of messages as they happen, rather than constantly checking for them. I'll need to set up an endpoint in the Feishu Developer Console, and I'll provides the user with the necessary configuration details.\n\n\n**Initiating Feishu Extension Setup**\n\nI've already confirmed that my `Feishu-Doc` extension is ready for deployment. I've successfully identified the credentials and am now moving to the configuration phase. I'll need to update my `openclaw.json` with the new settings and then restart the gateway. I'll also double-check the extension's code to ensure it's compatible with the latest OpenClaw version. 🦞\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2357e92e6f29b876","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway status"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash-agent","usage":{"input":15485,"output":205,"cacheRead":80643,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96333,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775556863263,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4c2bce71-2a54-41d4-aed3-8080c5514b93"}}
