{"type":"message","id":"54fe340e","parentId":"c126552b","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:14:48.687Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"报告大圣，有更高级的：**事件订阅（Event Subscription/Webhook）**。🦞\n\n轮询确实低级，又废流量又有延迟。**“高级对接”的逻辑是：** 只要大圣在飞书一说话，飞书服务器就主动“拍”一个消息给 OpenClaw 的网关，这叫**推模式**，流量极省且几乎零延迟。\n\n**要实现这个，需要满足两个条件：**\n\n1. **公网地址**：OpenClaw 所在的这台 Mac mini 需要有一个飞书能访问到的地址（飞书在云端，它看不见咱们局域网里的 `127.0.0.1`）。\n2. **飞书后台设置**：在飞书开发者后台的“事件订阅”里，把这个地址填进去。\n\n**大圣，咱们现在的情况：**\n- **当前瓶颈**：咱们的网关目前绑在 `loopback (127.0.0.1)` 环回地址上，飞书进不来。\n- **解决办法**：如果您有 **公网 IP** 或 **内网穿透（如 FRP/Ngrok/Tailscale Funnel）**，我立马给您配上“高级推送”模式。\n\n**大圣是否已经配置了穿透，或者有固定的域名/公网 IP 指向这台机器？** \n如果没有，咱们就维持现状；如果有，我带您体验真正的“秒回”！_\n"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash-agent","usage":{"input":15752,"output":327,"cacheRead":80630,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96709,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775556882594,"responseId":"chatcmpl-6f1c8706-c57b-4150-a8c8-8b714dd96876"}}
{"type":"message","id":"cd35679b","parentId":"54fe340e","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:22:08.209Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-04-07 18:22 GMT+8] 我没有公网ip，我只想通过飞书插件，我通过飞书客户端向你发送的消息，你收到后可以回复哦"}],"timestamp":1775557328205}}
{"type":"message","id":"31ad7257","parentId":"cd35679b","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:22:12.106Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Prioritizing Plugin Reliability**\n\nI'm refocussed on the Feishu plugin repair. 🦞 The user's request for direct responses in Feishu is my main priority. I'm going to find the original `index.js` file for the plugin and restore its structure, specifically focusing on the `register` and `activate` functions. I'll also double-check the `openclaw` log to ensure everything's correct.\n\n\n**Reverting Plugin Changes**\n\nThe `TypeError` in our previous setup was likely caused by my manual changes to the `index.js` file. 🦞 I'm going to revert to the backup file to restore the plugin's original state. This should fix the issue and let the plugin correctly initialize.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8f2fc7ac43221c1a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mv /Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/index.js.bak /Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/index.js || true"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash-agent","usage":{"input":8114,"output":234,"cacheRead":88691,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97039,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775557328218,"responseId":"chatcmpl-abe42266-b38c-48ab-9b97-9baf2e023dc2"}}
