{"type":"message","id":"69b08a40","parentId":"9e9f9568","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:22:16.641Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Recovering Plugin Entry**\n\nI'm refocussed on the Feishu plugin repair. 🦞 The original `index.js` file for Feishu was missing `register` and `activate` exports, which caused the initialization error. I'm going to rewrite `index.js` with the correct `loadBundledEntryExportSync` call, using `import.meta.url` for the correct path. This should fix the issue and let the plugin correctly initialize.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ec14398778d25c6d","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/index.js","content":"import { r as loadBundledEntryExportSync, t as defineBundledChannelEntry } from \"../../channel-entry-contract-DyY5TZkc.js\";\n\nconst feishu_default = defineBundledChannelEntry({\n\tid: \"feishu\",\n\tname: \"Feishu\",\n\tdescription: \"Bundled Feishu/Lark channel plugin\",\n\tloadBundledEntrySync() {\n\t\treturn loadBundledEntryExportSync(import.meta, \"./channel-entry.js\");\n\t}\n});\n\nexport { feishu_default as default };\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash-agent","usage":{"input":8468,"output":271,"cacheRead":88687,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97426,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775557332163,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4bea5afd-1529-4bd0-b566-a7931d33fbd6"}}
