{"type":"message","id":"400318f6","parentId":"1b68016d","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:27:49.379Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Standardizing Feishu Interaction**\n\nThe current Feishu plugin is failing to load, and it's also restricted to \"internal\" use. 🦞 I'm going to set up a small \"Bot Connector\" script that will bypass the broken plugin and directly handle messaging and polling. This will provide a more stable and efficient experience for the user.\n\n\n**Initiating Bot Connector Setup**\n\nI'm developing a robust \"Bot Connector\" for Feishu. 🦞 This Python script will act as a central hub, managing message polling and relaying them to me for processing. It'll also handle my responses back to the user on Feishu, ensuring our conversation is seamless.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c92cfed8de2e2bfa","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/auto_reply_bot.py","content":"import os\nimport requests\nimport json\nimport time\nfrom dotenv import load_dotenv\n\nload_dotenv()\n\n# 常量\nAPP_ID = \"cli_a95e7a8914ba5cc2\"\nAPP_SECRET = \"FnzZDL7YmMnFB2Pr1rXovcitjz6Cv13V\"\n\ndef get_tenant_access_token():\n    url = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\"\n    data = {\"app_id\": APP_ID, \"app_secret\": APP_SECRET}\n    res = requests.post(url, json=data).json()\n    return res.get(\"tenant_access_token\")\n\ndef send_reply(token, msg_id, content):\n    url = f\"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages/{msg_id}/reply\"\n    headers = {\"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {token}\", \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\"}\n    data = {\"msg_type\": \"text\", \"content\": json.dumps({\"text\": content})}\n    requests.post(url, headers=headers, json=data)\n\ndef poll_and_auto_reply():\n    token = get_tenant_access_token()\n    # 先获取 chat_id\n    chats_url = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/chats\"\n    headers = {\"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {token}\"}\n    chats = requests.get(chats_url, headers=headers).json()\n    \n    if not chats.get(\"data\", {}).get(\"items\"):\n        return\n        \n    chat_id = chats[\"data\"][\"items\"][0][\"chat_id\"]\n    last_processed_time = int(time.time() * 1000)\n    \n    print(\"🦞 龙虾飞书自动对话引擎已启动...\")\n    \n    while True:\n        try:\n            token = get_tenant_access_token() # 刷新 token\n            msgs_url = f\"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?container_id_type=chat&container_id={chat_id}\"\n            headers = {\"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {token}\"}\n            msgs = requests.get(msgs_url, headers=headers).json()\n            \n            for m in msgs.get(\"data\", {}).get(\"items\", []):\n                m_time = int(m.get(\"create_time\"))\n                if m_time > last_processed_time and m.get(\"sender\", {}).get(\"sender_type\") == \"user\":\n                    user_text = json.loads(m.get(\"content\")).get(\"text\")\n                    msg_id = m.get(\"message_id\")\n                    print(f\"💬 收到飞书指令: {user_text}\")\n                    \n                    # 模拟回答测试\n                    reply_text = f\"【龙虾自动回执】大圣，我收到您的指令了：『{user_text}』。链路完全畅通！🦞\"\n                    send_reply(token, msg_id, reply_text)\n                    print(f\"✅ 已回复飞书\")\n                    \n                    last_processed_time = m_time\n            \n            time.sleep(2)\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"⚠️ 飞书监听异常: {e}\")\n            time.sleep(5)\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    poll_and_auto_reply()\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash-agent","usage":{"input":683,"output":1000,"cacheRead":96707,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98390,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775557660753,"responseId":"chatcmpl-cf7ef781-d0c0-4b02-9fab-d7881ea1ef3b"}}
