{"type":"message","id":"d9e3494e","parentId":"79a16cf2","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:27:52.557Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Verifying Bot Connectivity**\n\nOkay, I'm launching the `auto_reply_bot.py` script now. 🦞 This will confirm if I can receive and reply to messages on Feishu, effectively bypassing the broken plugin. If this test succeeds, I'll have a reliable way to communicate with the user, even while we work on a more permanent fix for the plugin.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2ef49745dab1402d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"/usr/bin/python3 /Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/auto_reply_bot.py","background":true}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash-agent","usage":{"input":17515,"output":124,"cacheRead":80590,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98229,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775557669418,"responseId":"chatcmpl-e0c2d24b-d876-45e8-8584-74ab619eb661"}}
