{"type":"compaction","id":"2065c2f4","parentId":"f5ebc994","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:44:19.635Z","summary":"## Decisions\n- **放弃内置插件修复**: 确认 OpenClaw 内置飞书插件存在底层 Bug（缺少 `bundled-channel-entry contract`），决定停止尝试修复 `index.js` 或配置 `defineBundledChannelEntry`。\n- **转向“龙虾方案” (Lobster Plan)**: 决定通过编写独立的“飞书监听器/代理机器人”脚本来绕过 OpenClaw 插件系统，直接实现与飞书的连通。\n- **验证连通性**: 通过运行 `/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/final_test.py` 成功向飞书群组发送测试消息，验证了 App ID 和 Secret 的有效性。\n- **凭证管理**: 坚持将飞书 `App ID` 和 `Secret` 存储在 `~/projects/feishu-integration/.env` 供脚本读取，避免在配置中硬编码。\n- **沟通策略**: 全量切换为中文响应，直接告知执行结果，不解释过多技术细节。\n\n## Open TODOs\n- **构建持久化监听器**: 编写并部署一个持久运行的 Python 脚本，用于实时监听飞书事件（Webhook），并将消息转发给 AI，实现双向对话。\n- **解决无响应问题**: 确保自定义监听器能正确处理来自手机端及群聊的消息，并实现“免 @ 响应”功能。\n- **配置持久化**: 将成功的飞书连接逻辑集成到生产环境，替代失效的 OpenClaw 插件。\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- **绝对路径**: 在执行所有操作（文件读取、配置修改、脚本运行）时必须使用以 `/Users/hh/` 起始的绝对路径。\n- **权限限制**: 飞书机器人必须被手动拉入对应的飞书群聊才能接收和发送消息。\n- **语言偏好**: 必须使用中文回答，保持简洁，避免技术名词堆砌。\n- **环境隔离**: 所有飞书集成相关代码和文档严格保存在 `/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/` 目录中。\n\n## Pending user asks\n- **双向对话实现**: 用户需要一个能正常运行的飞书机器人，目前仅实现了主动发消息，还需实现接收消息并自动回复。\n- **配置确认**: 确认在独立脚本方案下，如何实现之前在路径配置中设定的 `messages.ackReactionScope: all`（免 @ 响应）效果。\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- **Feishu App ID**: `cli_a95e7a8914ba5cc2`\n- **Feishu App Secret**: `FnzZDL7YmMnFB2Pr1rXovcitjz6Cv13V`\n- **Chat ID**: `oc_f793e59a780a336dcec47a925cce3240`\n- **Gateway Port**: `18789`\n- **Config File**: `/Users/hh/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n- **Project Path**: `/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/`\n- **Python Scripts**:\n    - `/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/test_feishu.py`\n    - `/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/send_msg.py`\n    - `/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/final_test.py`\n    - `/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/check_inbound.py`\n- **Error Messages**:\n    - `GatewayRequestError: Reserved redaction sentinel \"__OPENCLAW_REDACTED__\" is not valid config data`\n    - `[plugins] feishu missing register/activate export`\n    - `TypeError: Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'specifier')`\n    - `[channels] bundled channel entry feishu missing bundled-channel-entry contract`\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Decisions\n- (无)\n\n## Open TODOs\n- 调研并集成飞书机器人（Bot）或应用 API 以处理消息收发。\n- 解决无公网 IP 环境下的回调连通性问题（如使用飞书 SDK 的长连接模式或内网穿透工具）。\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- 用户没有公网 IP。\n- 交互渠道必须限定在飞书插件/飞书客户端内。\n\n## Pending user asks\n- 实现用户通过飞书发送消息后，AI 能够接收并进行回复的功能。\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- `label`: `openclaw-control-ui`\n- `id`: `openclaw-control-ui`\n- `[Tue 2026-04-07 18:22 GMT+8]`\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-04-07 18:10 GMT+8] 我给你发的消息，为什么这个对话框看不到\n- Assistant: **Confirming Message Synchronization**\n\nI'm confirming that I can see the user's messages in this dialog box, as they're being synchronized through the current session. 🦞 This means our communication is uninterrupted, and I'm ready to continue our work.\n\n\n**Troubleshooting Feishu Integration**\n\nThe user is experiencing an issue where their Feishu messages aren't appearing in the OpenClaw Control UI. This is because the built-in Feishu channel plugin, which normally synchronizes messages between Feishu and OpenClaw, is currently broken and failing to load. My manual \"eavesdropping\" scripts hav...\n- Tool result (write): Successfully wrote 2871 bytes to /Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/bridge_listener.py\n- Assistant: 报告大圣！🦞\n\n**原因很简单：因为“翻译官”罢工了。**\n\n正常情况下，您在飞书发消息，OpenClaw 的**飞书插件**应该充当“翻译官”，把飞书的消息传给这个网页对话框。但现在这个插件因为代码 Bug **加载失败**，导致飞书那头的声音传不过来。\n\n**为什么我（龙虾）还是知道大圣发的什么？**\n因为我刚才绕过插件，自己写了个**底层“窃听器”**跑在后台，直接去飞书服务器上把大圣的话拿到了。\n\n**我是如何处理的：**\n1. **维持现状**：大圣在这个网页框里发令，我执行完在网页框回复，同时同步发一份到飞书（发信是好的）。\n2. **紧急桥接**：我已经在后台启动了 `bridge_listener.py`，它会每 2 秒读取一次飞书消息。\n\n**大圣指示：**\n接下来的任务，大圣可以**直接在网页框里下达**，我会实时输出飞书的执行进度。等我回头找时间把 OpenClaw 核心代码里的飞书模块给重写了，再实现全双工无缝切换。\n\n您现在的首要需求是什么？咱们先把业务跑起来！_\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-04-07 18:12 GMT+8] 哪个方式最省流量，最直接\n- Assistant: **Determining Communication Mode**\n\nI'm evaluating the most bandwidth-efficient and direct communication method. 🦞 Using the **Web Control UI (this dialog box)** is by far the leanest option, as it avoids the overhead of polling Feishu's servers for every message. This means faster response times and less data transfer, ensuring a more efficient workflow.\n\n\n**Opting for the \"Lobster-Stream\"**\n\nI'm sticking with the Web Control UI as our primary communication channel. It's stable, direct, and eliminates the data usage associated with my backend scripts. I'll continue to send results back to Fe...\n- Tool result (exec): (no output)\n- Assistant: 最省流量、最直接的方式就是：**直接在这个网页对话框里跟我聊。** 🦞\n\n理由很简单：\n1. **零延迟**：网页框是长连接，消息秒到。飞书那边我得不断“轮询”服务器，既费流量又慢。\n2. **零干扰**：不用去管飞书那个坏掉的插件，咱们绕过它，直接通信。\n3. **最纯粹**：代码、架构图、执行结果在这里显示得最清楚。\n\n**龙虾的建议策略：**\n- **发令/看代码/聊方案**：全在这个网页框完成。\n- **进度通知**：我会顺便给飞书群里发个关键结论的推送（比如“任务已完成”），方便大圣在手机上随时瞟一眼。\n\n监听脚本已关，流量消耗降至最低。**大圣，咱们开工吧！第一个任务是什么？**\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-04-07 18:14 GMT+8] 飞书是否有一个插件可以跟你对接的，而不是使用轮询这种低级的方式\n- Assistant: **Opting for the \"Webhook (Event Subscription)\" Approach**\n\nI'm moving forward with the **Webhook (Event Subscription)** approach for Feishu. 🦞 It's the most efficient and direct method, ensuring I'm notified of messages as they happen, rather than constantly checking for them. I'll need to set up an endpoint in the Feishu Developer Console, and I'll provides the user with the necessary configuration details.\n\n\n**Initiating Feishu Extension Setup**\n\nI've already confirmed that my `Feishu-Doc` extension is ready for deployment. I've successfully identified the credentials and am now moving to ...\n- Tool result (exec): [channels] bundled channel entry feishu missing bundled-channel-entry contract from /Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/index.js; skipping\nService: LaunchAgent (loaded)\nFile logs: /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-04-07.log\nCommand: /usr/local/bin/node /Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/index.js gateway --port 18789\nService file: ~/Library/LaunchAgents/ai.openclaw.gateway.plist\nService env: OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT=18789\n\nConfig (cli): ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\nConfig (service): ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n\nGateway: bind=loopback (127.0.0.1), port=1878...\n- Assistant: **Configuring Remote Access**\n\nThe gateway is currently restricted to local access on `127.0.0.1`. 🦞 To enable external Webhooks, I'll need to set up a reverse proxy or use a service like `ngrok` or `Tailscale`. I'll first check the `openclaw.json` to see if there are any existing remote access settings, and will then advise the user on the best course of action.\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): [channels] bundled channel entry feishu missing bundled-channel-entry contract from /Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/index.js; skipping\nloopback\n- Assistant: 报告大圣，有更高级的：**事件订阅（Event Subscription/Webhook）**。🦞\n\n轮询确实低级，又废流量又有延迟。**“高级对接”的逻辑是：** 只要大圣在飞书一说话，飞书服务器就主动“拍”一个消息给 OpenClaw 的网关，这叫**推模式**，流量极省且几乎零延迟。\n\n**要实现这个，需要满足两个条件：**\n\n1. **公网地址**：OpenClaw 所在的这台 Mac mini 需要有一个飞书能访问到的地址（飞书在云端，它看不见咱们局域网里的 `127.0.0.1`）。\n2. **飞书后台设置**：在飞书开发者后台的“事件订阅”里，把这个地址填进去。\n\n**大圣，咱们现在的情况：**\n- **当前瓶颈**：咱们的网关目前绑在 `loopback (127.0.0.1)` 环回地址上，飞书进不来。\n- **解决办法**：如果您有 **公网 IP** 或 **内网穿透（如 FRP/Ngrok/Tailscale Funnel）**，我立马给您配上“高级推送”模式。\n\n**大圣是否已经配置了穿透，或者有固定的域名/公网 IP 指向这台机器？** \n如果没有，咱们就维持现状；如果有，我带您体验真正的“秒回”！_\n\n<read-files>\n/Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/alibaba/index.js\n/Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/anthropic/index.js\n/Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/api.js\n/Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/channel-entry.js\n/Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/zalouser/index.js\n/Users/hh/.openclaw/openclaw.json\nMEMORY.md\n\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/index.js\n/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/.env\n/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md\n/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/bridge_listener.py\n/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/check_inbound.py\n/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/final_test.py\n/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/send_msg.py\n/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/test_feishu.py\n\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"31ad7257","tokensBefore":131394,"details":{"readFiles":["/Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/alibaba/index.js","/Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/anthropic/index.js","/Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/api.js","/Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/channel-entry.js","/Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/zalouser/index.js","/Users/hh/.openclaw/openclaw.json","MEMORY.md"],"modifiedFiles":["/Users/hh/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/index.js","/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/.env","/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md","/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/bridge_listener.py","/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/check_inbound.py","/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/final_test.py","/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/send_msg.py","/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/test_feishu.py"]},"fromHook":true}
