{"type":"message","id":"7ee9447d","parentId":"7dfc9a6c","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:44:25.703Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_61f0d2f9d6579f02","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"memory/2026-04-07.md","content":"\n## 2026-04-07 飞书集成进度记录\n\n### 关键进展\n1. **官方插件安装**：执行了 `npx -y @larksuite/openclaw-lark-tools install`，安装了 `openclaw-lark` 扩展。\n2. **配置迁移**：\n    - 废弃了之前损坏的内置 `feishu` 插件。\n    - 将 `Cli ID` 和 `Secret` 配置到了 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 的 `plugins.entries[\"openclaw-lark\"]` 中。\n3. **自建桥接器 (Lobster Bot)**：\n    - 在 `/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/auto_reply_bot.py` 部署了基于轮询的增强版自动回复引擎，作为插件失效时的兜底方案。\n    - 解决了 `NoneType` 和 JSON 解析等稳定性问题。\n\n### 当前状态\n- **控制链路**：网页端（OpenClaw Control UI）作为主控。\n- **飞书链路**：正在验证 `openclaw-lark` 插件的激活状态。自建 Bot 已在后台运行，理论上大圣在飞书发消息，Bot 会进行回执。\n\n### 遗留任务\n- 确认 `openclaw-lark` 插件是否已经完全接管消息流。\n- 如果插件正常，则停用 `/Users/hh/projects/feishu-integration/auto_reply_bot.py` 以节省系统资源。\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash-agent","usage":{"input":18444,"output":374,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18818,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775558659677,"responseId":"chatcmpl-35e7b5ff-eec7-4224-a4d8-140f48574140"}}
